-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>4-Color Process</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">4-Color Process is only available on outer canopy panels or valances. It cannot be used in other locations.\r\n\r\nMinimum 12 PRINTS per setup, which can be achieved with 2 or more patio umbrellas. Alternatively, you can choose to not use all 12 prints, but the pricing will have the same minimum costs. The run charge cannot go below a minimum of $270.00(G). Minimum cost is $566.00(G) for a panel print and/or $416.00(G) for a valance print.\r\n\r\nImprint area maximum is 12.75&quot;W x 12.75&quot;H for panel prints, and 12.75&quot;W x 5&quot;H for valance prints (this supersedes listed imprint areas on our entire patio umbrella line).\r\n\r\nPatio bases sold separately.\r\n\r\nPMS matching does not apply to Process printing since Pantone Coated inks are not used like in screenprinting. You can still choose to provide us with PMS numbers, as a reference.\r\n\r\nRush orders are not available with Process printing.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">DI-4CP</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>4-Color Process</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><p class=\"mb-3 text-[13px] leading-relaxed text-neutral-700\">4-Color Process is only available on outer umbrella canopy panels. It cannot be used with undercanopy printing, wide tie printing, or case printing.\r\n\r\nProcess color is not available for the SB-4675, SB-4676, or SB-4677 due to the special 2-ply fabric.\r\n\r\nPMS matching does not apply to Process printing since Pantone Coated inks are not used like in screenprinting. You may still provide us with PMS numbers as a reference.\r\n\r\nRush orders are not available with process color printing.\r\n\r\nArt-related restrictions may apply, such as minimum line weights or clear space requirements.\r\n\r\nPrice breaks for process color run charges are calculated per logo. We do not combine run charges to meet higher price breaks.\r\n\r\nEQP pricing applies to products only. Setups and run charges are excluded from those calculations.</p><p class=\"text-[13px] text-neutral-700\">DI-4CP</p></div>\n</details>\n<details class=\"group border-b border-neutral-200 last:border-b-0 open:bg-neutral-50/50\">\n<summary class=\"cursor-pointer list-none py-3 pl-1 pr-2 text-[13px] font-semibold text-neutral-900 outline-none [&::-webkit-details-marker]:hidden\">\n<span class=\"flex items-start justify-between gap-3\">\n<span>1st Imprint Color</span>\n<span class=\"mt-0.5 shrink-0 text-[10px] font-normal text-neutral-400 transition group-open:rotate-180\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▼</span>\n</span>\n</summary>\n<div class=\"border-t border-neutral-100 bg-white px-1 pb-3 pt-2\"><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">DCI-PMS 021</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Orange</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">DCI-PMS 106</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Yellow</p></div><div class=\"border-b border-neutral-100 py-3 last:border-0\"><p class=\"font-semibold text-neutral-900\">DCI-PMS 125</p><p class=\"text-[12px] text-neutral-600\">Flat Gold</p></div><div class=\"bo